<br>
However, I honestly feel the level cap should NOT be raised. Continue with level 65, its high enough. PoP was a cool expansion, but it basically eliminated the entire old word, as defined as SoL, Kunar and classic Norrath.<br>
<br>
Keep level 65 as the top level, I mean, we toppled the gods themselves with level 65, were practically demigods. Tune conent for 65 and revamp some old stuff to accomodate this. I do not want to see level 70 and be funnled into the next expansions XP zones and be able to raid everything in PoP with 24 people. <br>
<br>
A good solid guild can already progress PoP with raids of 40, level 70 would simply break this.<br>
<br>
Expansion = good, mudflation is not. Utilizing the vast world already established and its accompanying lore = golden.<br>
<br>
